### 1. Setting Up Your Project

First, make sure you have Node.js and MongoDB installed. Then, create a new directory for your project:

```bash
mkdir RoomManagementSystem
cd RoomManagementSystem
npm init -y
```

Install the necessary packages:

```bash
npm install express mongoose body-parser cors
npm install --save react react-dom
npm install axios
